{{Infobox ethnic group |group = Russians in Lebanon |image = |caption = |poptime = |popplace = [[Beirut]] ([[Greater Beirut]]) |langs = [[Russian language|Russian]], [[Arabic language|Arabic]] ([[Lebanese Arabic]]) |rels = [[Russian Orthodox Church]] }}
'''Russians in Lebanon''' are people of [[Russia]]n origin residing in [[Lebanon]]. Most of them are Russian women married to Lebanese men. Almost all of which live in [[Beirut]]. Several [[Russia|Russian]] stores and restaurants were established in the past years.
