There has been many regnal '''styles of Serbian sovereigns'''.
==Middle Ages== {|class="wikitable" style="text-align:center" |- ! Shortened style ! Time |- | Prince of Serbia / the Serbs{{Cref2|a}} || {{circa}} 960– |- | Grand Prince of Serbia / the Serbs / all Rascian lands{{Cref2|b}} || 1112–1217 |- | King of Serbia / the Serbs{{Cref2|c}} || 1217–1345 |- | [[Emperor of the Serbs|Tsar of All Serbia, Bulgaria, Albania and Greece]] / All the Serbians, Bulgarians, Albanians and Greeks{{Cref2|d}} || 1345–71 (–89) |- | Despot of Serbia / Rascia{{Cref2|e}} || 1402–1543 |}
