==Modern== *"Prince of Serbia" (see [[Principality of Serbia]]), in use 1817–82 *"King of Serbia" (see [[Kingdom of Serbia]]), in use 1882–1918 *"King of Serbs, Croats and Slovenes" (see [[Kingdom of Serbs, Croats and Slovenes]]), in use 1918–29 *"King of Yugoslavia" (see [[Kingdom of Yugoslavia]]), in use 1929–45
